75
00:03:02,133 --> 00:03:05,968
<i>Overnight, normal human beings</i>
<i>like you and i</i>

76
00:03:05,968 --> 00:03:08,701
<i>and all the institutions</i>
<i>we've come to rely on</i>

77
00:03:08,701 --> 00:03:10,534
