78
00:03:14,834 --> 00:03:16,767
<i>The program wasn't perfect.</i>

79
00:03:16,767 --> 00:03:17,834
<i>People got sick.</i>

80
00:03:17,834 --> 00:03:18,968
<i>Some died.</i>

81
00:03:18,968 --> 00:03:21,234
<i>That was not our intent.</i>

82
00:03:21,234 --> 00:03:24,267
<i>But now it's gone,</i>

83
00:03:24,267 --> 00:03:26,167
<i>and the future</i>
<i>that we were trying to prevent</i>

84
00:03:26,167 --> 00:03:27,701
<i>is here,</i>

85
00:03:27,701 --> 00:03:30,067
<i>and we are not ready.</i>

86
00:03:30,067 --> 00:03:33,033
<i>I believe it comes down</i>
<i>to a question of power.</i>

87
00:03:33,033 --> 00:03:35,534
<i>Who is going to hold it?</i>

88
00:03:35,534 --> 00:03:37,033
<i>Us...</i>

89
00:03:37,033 --> 00:03:38,334
