104
00:04:19,100 --> 00:04:20,400
Something happened.
I... i changed.

105
00:04:20,400 --> 00:04:21,734
I don't know how.

106
00:04:21,734 --> 00:04:23,067
She just
walked in here.

107
00:04:23,067 --> 00:04:24,200
She knew my name.

108
00:04:24,200 --> 00:04:27,400
She seems to know
about you and lily.

109
00:04:27,400 --> 00:04:29,234
I don't know

110
00:04:29,234 --> 00:04:30,667
what game
you're playing here,

111
00:04:30,667 --> 00:04:31,934
and i don't care.

112
00:04:31,934 --> 00:04:34,534
Richard... richard.

113
00:04:38,234 --> 00:04:39,601
Lily.

114
00:04:40,868 --> 00:04:42,601
Lily!

115
00:04:42,601 --> 00:04:44,501
Lily?

116
00:04:44,501 --> 00:04:46,567
Is isabelle with you?

117
00:04:48,167 --> 00:04:49,667
Lily...

118
00:04:50,801 --> 00:04:52,133
lily.

119
00:04:52,133 --> 00:04:53,767
Are you all right?

120
00:04:53,767 --> 00:04:57,400
Oh, richard,
i must have fainted.

121
00:04:58,567 --> 00:05:00,067
Is isabelle with you?

122
00:05:01,400 --> 00:05:02,701
Who are you?

123
00:05:02,701 --> 00:05:04,300
Where's my wife?

124
00:05:04,300 --> 00:05:06,467
Richard, what are you
talking about?

125
00:05:06,467 --> 00:05:08,200
I'm lily, your wife.

126
00:05:09,300 --> 00:05:10,934
Why are you
looking at me like...

127
00:05:13,501 --> 00:05:15,701
oh, my god.

128
00:05:15,701 --> 00:05:17,067
Ma'am, i don't know who you are.

129
00:05:22,767 --> 00:05:24,767
Oh...

130
00:05:26,000 --> 00:05:27,567
oh, my god.

131
00:05:36,167 --> 00:05:37,634
No!

132
00:05:40,767 --> 00:05:44,634
Your blood pressure
is elevated...

133
00:05:44,634 --> 00:05:47,067
but i suppose
that's to be expected.

134
00:05:47,067 --> 00:05:49,567
Heart, lungs, reflexes...

135
00:05:49,567 --> 00:05:51,801
all within the normal range.

136
00:05:51,801 --> 00:05:53,734
Doctor,
you call this normal?

137
00:05:53,734 --> 00:05:55,567
Richard, i want
to see isabelle.

138
00:05:55,567 --> 00:05:56,801
Where is my daughter?

139
