She's right outside.

140
00:05:58,234 --> 00:05:59,901
I'll bring her in
in a minute.

141
00:05:59,901 --> 00:06:01,601
I realize
how alarming this must be,

142
00:06:01,601 --> 00:06:03,033
but at least
you can take some solace

143
00:06:03,033 --> 00:06:04,334
in the fact that your wife

144
00:06:04,334 --> 00:06:06,234
is a perfectly healthy
older woman.

145
00:06:06,234 --> 00:06:09,167
If i had to guess,
i'd say she's about 75.

146
00:06:09,167 --> 00:06:10,734
I'm 29...

147
00:06:10,734 --> 00:06:12,267
and i don't understand.

148
00:06:12,267 --> 00:06:13,734
Please help me understand.

149
00:06:13,734 --> 00:06:16,367
How could
this happen?

150
00:06:16,367 --> 00:06:18,767
Maybe it's a reaction

151
00:06:18,767 --> 00:06:21,067
to being taken off
the promicin inhibitor,

152
00:06:21,067 --> 00:06:22,901
but truthfully,
i don't know.

153
00:06:22,901 --> 00:06:25,434
There is a condition
called progeria.

154
00:06:25,434 --> 00:06:27,467
It's associated
with rapid aging.

155
00:06:27,467 --> 00:06:29,834
So this kind of thing

156
00:06:29,834 --> 00:06:31,300
has happened before?

157
00:06:31,300 --> 00:06:33,234
Mr. Tyler...

158
00:06:33,234 --> 00:06:35,067
