and trying to determine
who knew what when.

180
00:07:59,667 --> 00:08:02,534
I will save this committee
the trouble and expense

181
00:08:02,534 --> 00:08:04,400
of a long investigation.

182
00:08:04,400 --> 00:08:07,133
The inhibitor program
was my idea.

183
00:08:07,133 --> 00:08:09,868
I was proud to lead it.

184
00:08:09,868 --> 00:08:13,300
The men on this board
were simply following my orders.

185
00:08:13,300 --> 00:08:15,067
If there's blame
to be assigned,

186
00:08:15,067 --> 00:08:16,534
it's mine.

187
00:08:16,534 --> 00:08:19,934
Mine alone.

188
00:08:21,234 --> 00:08:22,801
Yeah, i know kyle
doesn't want to see me.

189
00:08:22,801 --> 00:08:24,167
Is there some way
we can force him to?

190
00:08:24,167 --> 00:08:25,267
I'm his father.

191
00:08:25,267 --> 00:08:27,200
I want to know
how he's doing.

192
00:08:27,200 --> 00:08:28,501
Look, i realize you're trying,

193
00:08:28,501 --> 00:08:30,501
but it'll be months
before he goes to trial.

194
00:08:30,501 --> 00:08:32,033
I mean, you really think

195
00:08:32,033 --> 00:08:33,467
people are going to let ryland
position himself

196
00:08:33,467 --> 00:08:35,133
