of patriotic martyr?

197
00:08:35,133 --> 00:08:38,234
The man headed a conspiracy
that caused 28 deaths.

198
00:08:38,234 --> 00:08:39,434
Well, he says
it was accidental.

199
00:08:39,434 --> 00:08:40,834
A significant percentage
of this country

200
00:08:40,834 --> 00:08:41,968
believes him.

201
00:08:41,968 --> 00:08:43,234
Try "overwhelming."

202
00:08:43,234 --> 00:08:44,501
You guys listened
to talk radio lately?

203
00:08:44,501 --> 00:08:47,067
