206
00:08:49,767 --> 00:08:51,033
Maybe they should put him up

207
00:08:51,033 --> 00:08:53,067
for the nobel peace prize.

208
00:08:53,067 --> 00:08:54,300
Just tell him
i need to see him.

209
00:08:54,300 --> 00:08:55,567
We don't have to talk
about the case.

210
00:08:55,567 --> 00:08:57,634
I just have to see my son.

211
00:09:00,133 --> 00:09:02,534
Just ask him one more time,
okay?

212
00:09:02,534 --> 00:09:04,634
And...
and tell him we love him.

213
00:09:07,133 --> 00:09:08,767
Give him some time, thomas.

214
00:09:08,767 --> 00:09:10,701
Kyle needs to live
with his choice for a while.

215
00:09:12,501 --> 00:09:15,534
We're back.

216
00:09:15,534 --> 00:09:17,167
Tom...

217
00:09:17,167 --> 00:09:19,133
