222
00:09:40,801 --> 00:09:42,834
Members of the press,
i was including you

223
00:09:42,834 --> 00:09:44,300
in that "ladies
and gentlemen"

224
00:09:44,300 --> 00:09:45,367
designation.

225
00:09:45,367 --> 00:09:46,367
Thank you.

226
00:09:46,367 --> 00:09:48,901
Mr. Ryland,

227
00:09:48,901 --> 00:09:50,601
i'd like to pick up
the questioning

228
00:09:50,601 --> 00:09:52,100
