229
00:09:52,100 --> 00:09:54,567
You insist that you alone
gave the go-ahead

230
00:09:54,567 --> 00:09:56,133
for the promicin inhibitor
program.

231
00:09:56,133 --> 00:09:57,267
Is that right, sir?

232
00:09:57,267 --> 00:09:58,334
Yes, sir.

233
00:09:58,334 --> 00:09:59,634
It was my program all the way.

234
00:09:59,634 --> 00:10:02,667
So this committee
is to understand

235
00:10:02,667 --> 00:10:04,767
that your department
was able to plan and implement

236
00:10:04,767 --> 00:10:07,234
