on october 19th?

1039
00:46:29,408 --> 00:46:32,508
I guess you're going to have to
find yourself another telepath.

1040
00:46:38,307 --> 00:46:41,508
Good luck with that.

1041
00:46:41,508 --> 00:46:42,607
So you got nothing out of him?

1042
00:46:42,607 --> 00:46:44,007
Well, he told us
about hauser,

1043
00:46:44,007 --> 00:46:45,074
but as far as
the nova goes,

1044
00:46:45,074 --> 00:46:46,274
it's going to take time
to break him down.

1045
00:46:46,274 --> 00:46:47,474
How much time?

1046
00:46:47,474 --> 00:46:48,573
He's a telepath.

1047
00:46:48,573 --> 00:46:49,508
He knows what
we're thinking.

1048
00:46:49,508 --> 00:46:50,341
A little longer
than usual.

1049
00:46:50,341 --> 00:46:51,607
Okay, so it's not easy,

1050
00:46:51,607 --> 00:46:52,907
but gary navarro

1051
00:46:52,907 --> 00:46:54,640
has a level-seven
security clearance.

1052
00:46:54,640 --> 00:46:55,740
We have to assume
that he's been using it

1053
00:46:55,740 --> 00:46:56,874
to funnel
national secrets

1054
00:46:56,874 --> 00:46:57,940
to the nova group.

1055
00:46:57,940 --> 00:46:59,274
We need to know what he knows.

1056
00:46:59,274 --> 00:47:00,441
Now.

1057
00:47:00,441 --> 00:47:01,640
He'll talk.

1058
00:47:01,640 --> 00:47:02,774
Gary's been
inside our heads

1059
00:47:02,774 --> 00:47:04,174
for a year.

1060
00:47:04,174 --> 00:47:05,774
I think i know how to
get inside of his.

1061
00:47:10,707 --> 00:47:11,807
Careful with this.

1062
00:47:11,807 --> 00:47:13,441
Matthew.

1063
00:47:14,940 --> 00:47:16,341
I didn't expect
to see you back

1064
00:47:16,341 --> 00:47:17,640
for a couple of weeks.

1065
00:47:17,640 --> 00:47:19,441
The nova group revised
my calendar for me.

