00:47:19,441 --> 00:47:21,840
Wiped it clean, actually.

1067
00:47:21,840 --> 00:47:24,774
It's difficult to lobby
on behalf of the 4400

1068
00:47:24,774 --> 00:47:25,774
when some of them

1069
00:47:25,774 --> 00:47:27,441
are boasting
about their body count.

1070
00:47:27,441 --> 00:47:28,673
I suppose.

1071
00:47:28,673 --> 00:47:29,707
How's lily?

1072
00:47:29,707 --> 00:47:31,174
Any improvement
since i left?

1073
00:47:31,174 --> 00:47:32,840
If anything,
she's getting worse.

1074
00:47:32,840 --> 00:47:34,374
Sorry to hear that.

1075
00:47:34,374 --> 00:47:36,141
Isabelle?

1076
00:47:36,141 --> 00:47:37,241
She tried
to kill herself

1077
00:47:37,241 --> 00:47:38,640
this morning.

1078
00:47:39,907 --> 00:47:41,740
She jumped off the roof.

1079
00:47:41,740 --> 00:47:43,074
A few minutes later,

1080
00:47:43,074 --> 00:47:44,840
she was walking around
like nothing happened.

1081
00:47:44,840 --> 00:47:46,241
I got to tell you,
matthew...

1082
00:47:46,241 --> 00:47:47,241
i'm not going to lie.

1083
00:47:47,241 --> 00:47:49,740
I'm really glad
you're back.

1084
00:48:07,341 --> 00:48:10,007
[Knock on door]

1085
00:48:12,341 --> 00:48:16,074
Hello, isabelle.

1086
00:48:16,074 --> 00:48:18,041
Hello. Who are you?

1087
00:48:18,041 --> 00:48:20,707
My name is matthew ross.

1088
00:48:20,707 --> 00:48:23,074
I work closely with shawn.

1089
00:48:23,074 --> 00:48:24,940
I'm an advisor
to the 4400.

1090
00:48:24,940 --> 00:48:26,940
May i come in?

1091
00:48:35,707 --> 00:48:38,874
I understand there was
an incident this morning.

1092
00:48:38,874 --> 00:48:40,874
You attempted...

1093
00:48:40,874 --> 00:48:42,774
to harm yourself.

1094
00:48:44,807 --> 00:48:47,374
I see.

1095
00:48:50,007 --> 00:48:51,807
You had no right to do that!

1096
00:48:51,807 --> 00:48:53,840
Don't you understand
who you are?

1097
00:48:53,840 --> 00:48:55,940
What you're here to do?

1098
00:48:55,940 --> 00:48:57,041
No...

1099
00:48:57,041 --> 00:48:58,274
well, i do.

1100
00:48:58,274 --> 00:48:59,474
I know everything about you,
isabelle.

1101
00:48:59,474 --> 00:49:00,707
I know why you're here,

1102
00:49:00,707 --> 00:49:02,740
and i know
what you're supposed to do.

1103
00:49:03,907 --> 00:49:05,840
Sit...

1104
00:49:05,840 --> 00:49:08,441
and i'll tell you
a story.

1105
00:49:08,441 --> 00:49:09,673
You'll like it.

1106
00:49:09,673 --> 00:49:11,274
It's about your past,

1107
00:49:11,274 --> 00:49:12,907
and it's about your future.